Mom! Mom!

5
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:03,570
Get lost! Stop forcing me!

6
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,120
I know you want me to die.

7
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,320
Fine.

8
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,500
I'll grant your wish.

9
