12
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:08,800
Xu Nian.

13
00:02:16,329 --> 00:02:17,690
Long time no see, Xu Nian.

14
00:02:20,850 --> 00:02:21,810
What are you doing here?

15
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,270
You're not welcome here.

16
00:02:24,690 --> 00:02:26,760
I'm here to inform you on behalf of your father.

17
00:02:27,329 --> 00:02:29,550
Xinliang Group is facing financial difficulties.

18
00:02:29,650 --> 00:02:32,190
They can only get rid of some worthless assets,

19
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:34,360
including this special education school.

20
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:37,470
My mom founded the school.

21
00:02:37,770 --> 00:02:39,010
It never belonged to the group.

22
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,560
Who are you to sell it?

23
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,340
Although the school is not,

24
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:44,370
the land is.

25
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,460
I know you have some misunderstandings about me.

26
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,960
But this is your father's decision.

27
00:02:49,010 --> 00:02:50,820
You have been estranged from your father for so many years.

28
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,770
Why don't you go back with me and talk to him?

29
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,829
Okay, let's meet my dad.

30
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,010
Get in.

31
00:03:22,890 --> 00:03:23,570
What's wrong?

32
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:47,880
It's done.

33
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,890
Mr. Zhou, she's already in the room.

34
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:44,750
You promised to invest in Xinliang Group...

35
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:49,430
Mrs. Xu, you're really quick to get things done

36
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,820
No problem.

37
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,960
My stepdaughter won't scream no matter what you do to her.

38
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,690
Mr. Zhou, enjoy yourself.

39
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,080
Mr. Gu, your dinner is here.

40
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,050
Put it there.

41
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,560
She ran away. Go get her.

42
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,900
Stop! Stop!

43
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,840
Stop! Stop!

44
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,160
What took you so long?

45
00:07:06,610 --> 00:07:07,430
Room 1701.

46
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,240
A waiter is waiting for you at the door.

47
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:09,930
Okay.

48
00:07:16,810 --> 00:07:17,930
Did Mr. Gu ask you to come?

49
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,310
Alright, stop looking.

50
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:21,370
Go inside.

51
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:31,150
What are you doing here?

52
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:33,670
Who let you in?

53
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,590
Bad guys are after me! Help me!

54
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:46,920
Go!

55
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,100
Get out!

56
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,830
Have you found her?

57
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:53,900
No.

58
00:07:57,290 --> 00:07:58,610
Don't you understand me?

59
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:01,560
Get out! Get out!

60
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:02,480
Leave!

61
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:03,380
Leave!

62
00:08:03,410 --> 00:08:04,200
Get out!

63
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,460
You go this way.

64
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,400
You go this way. Keep looking.

65
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,110
Okay.

66
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:10,740
Go!

67
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,930
You must find her.
